Burberry Brit Eau De Parfum For Women_The Burberry Brit Eau De Parfum for Women is a green-oriental fragrance that comprises a blend of lush fruits, sweet nutty essences, soothing amber, vanilla and Tonka bean. The fresh and irresistible aroma is provided through sugared almond and lush white peony. The Burberry Brit fragrance intensifies with the inclusion of amber and mahogany, and is suitable for day and evening wear. This Burberry Brit perfume spray offers women a touch of sensuality and personality. The bottle is imprinted in a Burberry checked pattern.

